metadata.name: Edge(NFT+Physical work)
metadata.description:
Imaginary paradise - as soon as the opportunity presented itself, she fled from it, forever turning away from everything, as she believed, vulgar, embellished, pseudo-correct ... Life on the verge, no, everything is wrong it's not me ... I'm lost, is it a mask? no, who am I who am I?


Oil on canvas  size 100/80
first owner -physical work
